[0.007657, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m== 1. Eval harness — 25-record stratified slice of labeled_v300.jsonl ==\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[2mStratified sample: 15 duplicates + 10 novel. Full 300-record run is ~75s.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[2mThe slice keeps the demo under 2 minutes; the leaderboard.csv tail below has\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.007705, "o", "\u001b[2mthe real numbers from the full Phase 2.9 / 3.3 / 3.5 runs.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[2.034653, "o", "wrote 25 records to /tmp/priorart-demo-bench.jsonl (15 dup + 10 novel)\r\n"]
[2.038306, "o", "\u001b[2mRunning eval (dense_bge_m3 config, ~10-15s on the 25-record slice)...\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[14.396051, "o", "[eval] config=dense_bge_m3 benchmark=priorart-demo-bench.jsonl records=25 novel=10 thresholds=[0.5, 0.55, 0.6, 0.65, 0.7, 0.75, 0.8]\r\n[eval] ece=0.2641 bins=10 records_in_calibration=25 (25/25 non-errored)\r\n| **0.8** | **0.000** | **0.000** | **0.000** | **0.000** | **0.600** | **0.264** | **0.600** | **YES** |\r\nBest threshold (MRR-max under FPR ≤ 0.15): **0.8**\r\n[eval] done in 7.6s. search_errors=0 fpr_cap=0.15 best_threshold=0.8 (MRR=0.000, FPR-on-novel=0.600)\r\n🏃 View run dense_bge_m3 | priorart-demo-bench | corpus=2026-06-08 | t=0.80 | run=1782955760 at: http://localhost:15000/#/experiments/9/runs/36dd5ef64bee4ca0b808e3b4ef8d8d7a\r\n🧪 View experiment at: http://localhost:15000/#/experiments/9\r\n"]
